<p>This resource is control the look and feel for your current session. To be honest, this is to implement, rather than claim righteousness on; making sites easy to use for differing people.  As the range of options increases, I will express this in more needs centric vocabulary (i.e. expressed in medical terms).  I just hope people spot it and use it.  <em>This is a serious site, so you may not have comic sans.</em></p>


